<bibRefCitation id="1E73AF15A4A7F7C8DC62E7D6ED335033" author="Kifune, T" journalOrPublisher="Transactions of the Shikoku Entomological Society" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" pagination="135 - 138" refId="B49" refString="Kifune, T, Tano, T, 1991. A new host and new localities of Pseudoxenos piercei Schultze, 1925 in the Philippines. Strepsiptera Stylopidae Notulae Strepsipterologicae - 21. Transactions of the Shikoku Entomological Society 194: 135 - 138" title="A new host and new localities of Pseudoxenos piercei Schultze, 1925 in the Philippines. Strepsiptera Stylopidae Notulae Strepsipterologicae - 21." volume="194" year="1991">Kifune and Tano 1991</bibRefCitation>
